Invocation Name: brazil economy review
des:
Brazil Economy Review is an app that provides latest news and updates about Brazilian economy, agriculture, market and others.

Triggered by: Alexa, Brazil Economy Review.

All news (financial, economics, etc) are provided by the Brazilian Government (IBGE) from the source:
https://servicodados.ibge.gov.br/api/docs/noticias?versao=3

IBGE stands for: Brazilian Institute of Geography and Statistics
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
